OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,FITV News' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew, Producer Philip Sime and Camera
OL,8,FOperator Barnaby Green report from
OL,9,FSvalbard in the Arctic Circle
OL,11,FIn the lashing rain today, the
OL,12,Fenvironment 79 degrees north in Ny-
OL,13,FAlesund is brutal. It's also fragile.
OL,15,FThe nearest town on this island,
OL,16,FLongyearbyen, posted its warmest
OL,17,Fsummer on record today.
