OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,FIt's why climate research scientists
OL,7,Fare investigating how changes to
OL,8,Ftemperatures are impacting the local
OL,9,Fwildlife. Assessing how behaviours may
OL,10,Fchange, and if species can even
OL,11,Fsurvive.
OL,13,FMax Willems is a Dutch scientist
OL,14,Fworking for a German research team in
OL,15,FNorway. Her focus is on the Fjord, a
OL,16,Fnarrow body of water, and the fish who
OL,17,Fcall it home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
