OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,FThe surface temperature of the Fjord
OL,7,Fat this time of year is usually 5C,
OL,8,Fbut this year it's 7C. That may be a
OL,9,Fshort term blip but the long term
OL,10,Ftrend shows the waters are warming.
OL,12,FInside two controlled tanks, small
OL,13,Ffish are swimming against a current.
OL,14,F"We are giving the fish a fitness
OL,15,Ftest," Max tells me.
OL,17,FThe current speeds up and oxygen
OL,18,Flevels in the water are monitored to
OL,19,Fsee how hard the fish are having to
OL,20,Fwork.
