OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,F"I think if everyone bands together
OL,7,Fand we try to limit the increase of
OL,8,Fwater temperature amongst other
OL,9,Fpollutants and things like that ...
OL,10,Fthey can maintain. They are pretty
OL,11,Fsturdy guys."
OL,13,FGrazing behind a nearby building is a
OL,14,Fwild reindeer. Vegetation is easy to
OL,15,Fcome by in the summer. In the winter
OL,16,Fthey dig through snow to access
OL,17,Fgreenery. The problem is ice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
