OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,FScientists are noticing an increase in
OL,7,Fwinter rain which freezes as a hard
OL,8,Flayer, impenetrable to hooves. The
OL,9,Ffear is this could lead to reindeers
OL,10,Fstarving over the long dark winter
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FEven accessing the scientific sites
OL,14,Fdotted around the outpost is
OL,15,Fincreasingly tricky.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
