OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,FThis is also polar bear country - it's
OL,7,Ftheir home and they are the apex
OL,8,Fpredators. Scientists have to carry
OL,9,Fguns as a last line of defence, but
OL,10,Fthe focus is on avoiding contact if
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,FFlare guns fire a loud warning and
OL,14,Frangers on radios coordinate to keep
OL,15,Fpeople and bears safe.
OL,17,FNo British scientist has ever had to
OL,18,Fshoot a bear here and they intend to
OL,19,Fkeep it that way. But sightings near
OL,20,FNy-Alesund seem to be on the up.
