OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,FThere were four sightings in the last
OL,7,Ffortnight alone including the rare
OL,8,Fsight of a bear killing a reindeer.
OL,10,F"I have only been here six years,"
OL,11,FHarbour Master Erland Havestrom tells
OL,12,Fme.
OL,14,F"That's, of course, a short
OL,15,Fperspective. But, when you hear the
OL,16,Fstories, you follow the research going
OL,17,Fon ... there is a change here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
