OL,3,CThe challenges of monitoring climate
OL,4,Cchange in the Arctic Circle
OL,6,F"There are more changes here now
OL,7,Fduring summer instead of wintertime,
OL,8,Flike the sea ice is gone, more or
OL,9,Fless. So, they're not here during
OL,10,Fspring hunting seals on the ice
OL,11,Fanymore.
OL,13,F"They're here during summer on the
OL,14,Fislands, eating bird eggs. That's a
OL,15,Fhuge change in behaviour locally here.
OL,16,FSo, something is changing for sure."
OL,18,FTomorrow we're heading out on foot to
OL,19,Fa nearby glacier retreating up the
OL,20,Fvalley.
